{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"About 15 years ago, I went to visit a friend in Hong Kong."},{"time":7000,"text":"And at the time I was very superstitious."},{"time":11000,"text":"So, upon landing -- this was still at the old Hong Kong airport"},{"time":16000,"text":"that's Kai Tak, when it was smack in the middle of the city --"},{"time":19000,"text":"I thought, \"If I see something good, I'm going to have a great time here in"},{"time":24000,"text":"my two weeks. And if I see something negative, I'm going to be miserable, indeed.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":32000,"text":"So the plane landed in between the buildings"},{"time":34000,"text":"and got to a full stop in front of this little billboard."},{"time":41000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":42000,"text":"And I actually went to see some of the design companies"},{"time":46000,"text":"in Hong Kong in my stay there."},{"time":48000,"text":"And it turned out that --"},{"time":50000,"text":"I just went to see, you know, what they are doing in Hong Kong."}]},{"cues":[{"time":55000,"text":"But I actually walked away with a great job offer."},{"time":59000,"text":"And I flew back to Austria, packed my bags,"},{"time":63000,"text":"and, another week later, I was again on my way to Hong Kong"},{"time":69000,"text":"still superstitions and thinking, \"Well, if that 'Winner' billboard is still up,"},{"time":76000,"text":"I'm going to have a good time working here."},{"time":78000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":79000,"text":"But if it's gone, it's going to be really miserable and stressful.\""},{"time":85000,"text":"So it turned out that not only was the billboard still up"},{"time":89000,"text":"but they had put this one right next to it."},{"time":91000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":94000,"text":"On the other hand, it also taught me where superstition gets me"},{"time":98000,"text":"because I really had a terrible time in Hong Kong."},{"time":100000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":103000,"text":"However, I did have a number of real moments of happiness in my life --"},{"time":114000,"text":"of, you know, I think what the conference brochure refers to"},{"time":119000,"text":"as \"moments that take your breath away.\""},{"time":122000,"text":"And since I'm a big list maker, I actually listed them all."},{"time":129000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":130000,"text":"Now, you don't have to go through the trouble of reading them"},{"time":133000,"text":"and I won't read them for you."},{"time":136000,"text":"I know that it's incredibly boring to hear about other people's happinesses."},{"time":140000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":142000,"text":"What I did do, though is, I actually looked at them from a design standpoint"},{"time":151000,"text":"and just eliminated all the ones that had nothing to do with design."},{"time":157000,"text":"And, very surprisingly, over half of them had, actually, something to do with design."}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"So there are, of course, two different possibilities."},{"time":167000,"text":"There's one from a consumer's point of view --"},{"time":169000,"text":"where I was happy while experiencing design."},{"time":172000,"text":"And I'll just give you one example. I had gotten my first Walkman."},{"time":176000,"text":"This is 1983."},{"time":178000,"text":"My brother had this great Yamaha motorcycle"},{"time":181000,"text":"that he was willing to borrow to me freely."},{"time":184000,"text":"And The Police's \"Synchronicity\""},{"time":187000,"text":"cassette had just been released"},{"time":189000,"text":"and there was no helmet law in my hometown of Bregenz."},{"time":192000,"text":"So you could drive up into the mountains"},{"time":194000,"text":"freely blasting The Police on the new Sony Walkman."},{"time":198000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":199000,"text":"And I remember it as a true moment of happiness."},{"time":204000,"text":"You know, of course, they are related to this combination of"},{"time":209000,"text":"at least two of them being, you know, design objects."},{"time":213000,"text":"And, you know, there's a scale of happiness when you talk about in design"},{"time":217000,"text":"but the motorcycle incident would definitely be, you know,"},{"time":221000,"text":"situated somewhere here -- right in there between Delight and Bliss."}]},{"cues":[{"time":227000,"text":"Now, there is the other part, from a designer's standpoint --"},{"time":233000,"text":"if you're happy while actually doing it."},{"time":235000,"text":"And one way to see how happy designers are when they're designing could be to"},{"time":242000,"text":"look at the authors' photos on the back of their monographs?"},{"time":246000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":247000,"text":"So, according to this, the Australians and the Japanese"},{"time":252000,"text":"as well as the Mexicans"},{"time":253000,"text":"are very happy."},{"time":255000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":256000,"text":"While, somewhat, the Spaniards ..."},{"time":258000,"text":"and, I think, particularly, the Swiss"},{"time":262000,"text":"(Laughter),"},{"time":264000,"text":"don't seem to be doing all that well."},{"time":266000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":274000,"text":"Last November, a museum opened in Tokyo called The Mori Museum,"},{"time":280000,"text":"in a skyscraper, up on the 56th floor."},{"time":284000,"text":"And their inaugural exhibit was called \"Happiness.\""},{"time":288000,"text":"And I went, very eagerly, to see it, because --"},{"time":292000,"text":"well, also, with an eye on this conference."},{"time":296000,"text":"And they interestingly sectioned the exhibit off into four different areas."},{"time":306000,"text":"Under \"Arcadia,\" they showed things like this, from the Edo period --"},{"time":310000,"text":"a hundred ways to write \"happiness\" in different forms."},{"time":315000,"text":"Or they had this apple by Yoko Ono -- that, of course, later on"},{"time":319000,"text":"was, you know, made into the label for The Beatles."}]},{"cues":[{"time":324000,"text":"Under \"Nirvana\" they showed this Constable painting."},{"time":328000,"text":"And there was a little -- an interesting theory about abstraction."},{"time":332000,"text":"This is a blue field -- it's actually an Yves Klein painting."},{"time":336000,"text":"And the theory was that if you abstract an image, you really, you know"},{"time":341000,"text":"open as much room for the un-representable --"},{"time":345000,"text":"and, therefore, you know, are able to involve the viewer more."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351000,"text":"Then, under \"Desire,\" they showed these Shunsho paintings --"},{"time":355000,"text":"also from the Edo period -- ink on silk."},{"time":361000,"text":"And, lastly, under \"Harmony,\" they had this 13th-century mandala from Tibet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":368000,"text":"Now, what I took away from the exhibit was that"},{"time":372000,"text":"maybe with the exception of the mandala"},{"time":375000,"text":"most of the pieces in there were actually about the visualization of happiness"},{"time":381000,"text":"and not about happiness."},{"time":383000,"text":"And I felt a little bit cheated, because the visualization --"},{"time":387000,"text":"that's a really easy thing to do."},{"time":390000,"text":"And, you know, my studio -- we've done it all the time."},{"time":393000,"text":"This is, you know, a book."},{"time":395000,"text":"A happy dog -- and you take it out, it's an aggressive dog."},{"time":399000,"text":"It's a happy David Byrne and an angry David Byrne."},{"time":405000,"text":"Or a jazz poster with a happy face and a more aggressive face."},{"time":409000,"text":"You know, that's not a big deal to accomplish."}]},{"cues":[{"time":413000,"text":"It has gotten to the point where, you know, within advertising"},{"time":418000,"text":"or within the movie industry, \"happy\" has gotten such a bad reputation that"},{"time":424000,"text":"if you actually want to do something with the subject"},{"time":427000,"text":"and still appear authentic, you almost would have to, you know,"},{"time":432000,"text":"do it from a cynical point of view."},{"time":435000,"text":"This is, you know, the movie poster."},{"time":438000,"text":"Or we, a couple of weeks ago, designed a box set for The Talking Heads"},{"time":443000,"text":"where the happiness visualized on the cover definitely has, very much, a dark side to it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":454000,"text":"Much, much more difficult is this, where the designs actually can evoke happiness --"},{"time":463000,"text":"and I'm going to just show you three that actually did this for me."},{"time":470000,"text":"This is a campaign done by a young artist in New York, who calls himself \"True.\""},{"time":476000,"text":"Everybody who has ridden the New York subway system will be"},{"time":479000,"text":"familiar with these signs?"},{"time":482000,"text":"True printed his own version of these signs."},{"time":486000,"text":"Met every Wednesday at a subway stop with 20 of his friends."},{"time":491000,"text":"They divided up the different subway lines and added their own version."},{"time":497000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":498000,"text":"So this is one."},{"time":500000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":506000,"text":"Now, the way this works in the system is that nobody ever looks at these signs."},{"time":511000,"text":"So you're"},{"time":513000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":514000,"text":"you're really bored in the subway, and you kind of stare at something."},{"time":519000,"text":"And it takes you a while until it actually --"},{"time":521000,"text":"you realize that this says something different than what it normally says."},{"time":525000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":527000,"text":"I mean, that's, at least, how it made me happy."},{"time":530000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":541000,"text":"Now, True is a real humanitarian."},{"time":545000,"text":"He didn't want any of his friends to be arrested,"},{"time":547000,"text":"so he supplied everybody with this fake volunteer card."},{"time":552000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":555000,"text":"And also gave this fake letter from the MTA to everybody --"},{"time":559000,"text":"sort of like pretending that it's an art project"},{"time":562000,"text":"financed by The Metropolitan Transit Authority."},{"time":564000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":566000,"text":"Another New York project."},{"time":569000,"text":"This is at P.S. 1 -- a sculpture that's basically a square room"},{"time":572000,"text":"by James Turrell, that has a retractable ceiling."},{"time":576000,"text":"Opens up at dusk and dawn every day."},{"time":579000,"text":"You don't see the horizon."},{"time":580000,"text":"You're just in there, watching the incredible, subtle changes of color in the sky."},{"time":587000,"text":"And the room is truly something to be seen."},{"time":592000,"text":"People's demeanor changes when they go in there."},{"time":597000,"text":"And, for sure, I haven't looked at the sky in the same way"},{"time":602000,"text":"after spending an hour in there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605000,"text":"There are, of course, more than those three projects that I'm showing here."},{"time":610000,"text":"I would definitely say that observing Vik Muniz' \"Cloud\""},{"time":614000,"text":"a couple of years ago in Manhattan for sure made me happy, as well."},{"time":618000,"text":"But my last project is, again, from a young designer in New York."},{"time":623000,"text":"He's from Korea originally."},{"time":624000,"text":"And he took it upon himself to print 55,000 speech bubbles --"},{"time":632000,"text":"empty speech bubbles stickers, large ones and small ones."},{"time":635000,"text":"And he goes around New York and just puts them, empty as they are, on posters."},{"time":640000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":642000,"text":"And other people go and fill them in."},{"time":645000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":648000,"text":"This one says, \"Please let me die in peace.\""},{"time":651000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":658000,"text":"I think that was --"},{"time":660000,"text":"the most surprising to myself was that the writing was actually so good."},{"time":665000,"text":"This is on a musician poster, that says:"},{"time":668000,"text":"\"I am concerned that my CD will not sell more than 200,000 units"},{"time":672000,"text":"and that, as a result, my recoupable advance"},{"time":676000,"text":"from my label will be taken from me,"},{"time":678000,"text":"after which, my contract will be cancelled,"},{"time":680000,"text":"and I'll be back doing Journey covers on Bleecker Street.\""},{"time":683000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":702000,"text":"I think the reason this works so well is because everybody involved wins."},{"time":707000,"text":"Jee gets to have his project;"},{"time":709000,"text":"the public gets a sweeter environment;"},{"time":713000,"text":"and different public gets a place to express itself;"},{"time":717000,"text":"and the advertisers finally get somebody to look at their ads."},{"time":721000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":728000,"text":"Well, there was a question, of course, that was on my mind for a while:"},{"time":734000,"text":"You know, can I do more of the things that I like doing in design"},{"time":739000,"text":"and less of the ones that I don't like to be doing?"},{"time":743000,"text":"Which brought me back to my list making --"},{"time":747000,"text":"you know, just to see what I actually like about my job."}]},{"cues":[{"time":750000,"text":"You know, one is: just working without pressure."},{"time":754000,"text":"Then: working concentrated, without being frazzled."},{"time":758000,"text":"Or, as Nancy said before, like really immerse oneself into it."},{"time":764000,"text":"Try not to get stuck doing the same thing --"},{"time":767000,"text":"or try not get stuck behind the computer all day."},{"time":771000,"text":"This is, you know, related to it: getting out of the studio."},{"time":775000,"text":"Then, of course, trying to, you know, work on things"},{"time":778000,"text":"where the content is actually important for me."},{"time":781000,"text":"And being able to enjoy the end results."}]},{"cues":[{"time":787000,"text":"And then I found another list in one of my diaries that actually contained"},{"time":795000,"text":"all the things that I thought I learned in my life so far."},{"time":799000,"text":"And, just about at that time, an Austrian magazine called and asked"},{"time":804000,"text":"if we would want to do six spreads -- design six spreads"},{"time":808000,"text":"that work like dividing pages between the different chapters in the magazine?"},{"time":813000,"text":"And the whole thing just fell together."},{"time":815000,"text":"So I just picked one of the things that I thought I learned --"},{"time":821000,"text":"in this case, \"Everything I do always comes back to me\" --"},{"time":824000,"text":"and we made these spreads right out of this."},{"time":827000,"text":"So it was: \"Everything"},{"time":829000,"text":"I do"},{"time":831000,"text":"always"},{"time":833000,"text":"comes"},{"time":834000,"text":"back"},{"time":836000,"text":"to me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":838000,"text":"A couple of weeks ago, a"},{"time":840000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":842000,"text":"French company asked us to design five billboards for them."},{"time":847000,"text":"Again, we could supply the content for it."},{"time":850000,"text":"So I just picked another one."},{"time":852000,"text":"And this was two weeks ago."},{"time":854000,"text":"We flew to Arizona -- the designer who works with me, and myself --"},{"time":860000,"text":"and photographed this one."},{"time":862000,"text":"So it's: \"Trying"},{"time":865000,"text":"to look"},{"time":866000,"text":"good"},{"time":868000,"text":"limits"},{"time":870000,"text":"my life.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":872000,"text":"And then we did one more of these."},{"time":875000,"text":"This is, again, for a magazine, dividing pages."},{"time":880000,"text":"This is: \"Having\" --"},{"time":881000,"text":"this is the same thing;"},{"time":882000,"text":"it's just, you know, photographed from the side."},{"time":885000,"text":"This is from the front."},{"time":886000,"text":"Then it's: \"guts.\""},{"time":888000,"text":"Again, it's the same thing -- \"guts\" is just the same room, reworked."},{"time":893000,"text":"Then it's: \"always"},{"time":895000,"text":"works out.\""},{"time":900000,"text":"Then it's \"for,\" with the light on."},{"time":903000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":905000,"text":"And it's \"me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":907000,"text":"Thank you so much."},{"time":909000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}